479
00:26:35,319 --> 00:26:40,079
We thank you for the privilege of being able to gather together this evening.

480
00:26:40,079 --> 00:26:46,759
I thank you for the opportunity to have some time in our service to hear and see what the

481
00:26:46,759 --> 00:26:51,439
children have learned this summer through this children's ministry.

482
00:26:51,439 --> 00:26:57,239
Lord, I'm thankful for the work that has been done, the labor that has been invested, the

483
00:26:57,239 --> 00:27:01,039
influence that has taken place in the lives of these young people.

484
00:27:01,039 --> 00:27:05,359
We think about the future generation of our church and at times if we're not careful,

485
00:27:05,359 --> 00:27:12,399
we can look at children as maybe making messes, getting in the way, but those are the future

486
00:27:12,399 --> 00:27:19,479
church members, church song leaders, preachers and instrumentalists and so on and so forth.

487
00:27:19,479 --> 00:27:23,679
And God, we thank you for the opportunity that we have to serve you together.

488
00:27:23,679 --> 00:27:26,519
We thank you for whatever opportunities you would give us.

489
00:27:26,519 --> 00:27:30,479
And I pray that as you would give us those opportunities, that we would serve you in

490
00:27:30,479 --> 00:27:35,279
the greatest capacity that we possibly could, that we would rely upon your power and your

491
00:27:35,279 --> 00:27:41,119
spirit, that we would do all that we do for your honor and for your glory, that you alone

492
00:27:41,119 --> 00:27:44,759
would receive the glory that is due unto your name.

493
00:27:44,759 --> 00:27:45,759
Thank you for our church.

494
00:27:45,759 --> 00:27:49,439
I thank you, God, for the opportunities that we have to serve you.

495
00:27:49,439 --> 00:27:51,519
I thank you for the various ministries.

496
00:27:51,519 --> 00:27:55,559
I thank you, God, for each individual that has served, that has given of their time and

497
00:27:55,559 --> 00:27:59,839
their talents in order to serve you and the capacity in which you have equipped them to

498
00:27:59,839 --> 00:28:00,839
do so.

499
00:28:00,839 --> 00:28:06,159
I pray, God, that you'd help us to understand the importance of laboring together with you.

500
00:28:06,159 --> 00:28:08,879
I thank you for enabling us and equipping us.

501
00:28:08,879 --> 00:28:11,199
I pray that you'd be glorified through our lives.

502
00:28:11,199 --> 00:28:15,119
Bless now as we respond to the time of invitation.

503
00:28:15,119 --> 00:28:19,879
Perhaps there's someone that, Lord, you're speaking to their heart about a particular

504
00:28:19,879 --> 00:28:20,879
area of service.

505
00:28:20,879 --> 00:28:26,359
And Lord, maybe there's something in someone's life that you've just touched in their heart

506
00:28:26,359 --> 00:28:29,639
and their life with regard to responding to you.

507
00:28:29,639 --> 00:28:33,159
And I pray, Lord, that we'd be doers of the word and not hearers only.

508
00:28:33,159 --> 00:28:34,880
And we'll thank you for the work that you'll do.

509
00:28:34,880 --> 00:28:36,319
For it's in Christ's name we pray.

510
00:28:36,319 --> 00:28:36,639
Would you stand?

